  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Acute brain injury

          -  Patient who receive an antibiotic for an infection or prophylaxy

          -  Glasgow coma score &lt; 8

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &lt; 18 years old

          -  Pregnant woman

          -  HCV, HIV, HBV infection
      </textblock>
